column2: Table 5#6#5AM1# Change in Private Inventories by Industry
[Millions of dollars; quarters seasonally adjusted at annual rates]
E=Quarterly data published in the Survey of Current Business monthly (NIPA table 5.6.5A),
monthly data are underlying detail to the published data.

vehicle dealers.  Beginning with 1981, these inventories are included in "other durable goods."
